user.biography:
Small family-owned toy shop. 
🍽 Every purchase helps provide meals for kids in need
📦 Flat-rate US shipping: $3.50
🌴 Based in Rancho Mission Viejo, CA

node.text: These felt flowers are stunning! 😍 We’ve been getting a lot of requests to make them available individually, so now there is an option to purchase each stem individually! They’re listed under the page “new”. 🧡
